author: WBAL NewsRadio 1090
title: Ravens Coach Harbaugh Monday Press Conference
text:
WBAL NewsRadio 1090 Credit: BaltimoreRavens.com 
Baltimore Ravens head coach John Harbaugh will hold his regular, in-season press conference Monday at 4 p.m. in the auditorium of the Under Armour Performance Center in Owings Mills. 
Coach Harbaugh is expect to speak on yesterday's loss to the the San Francisco 49ers and will look ahead to the next game against the Arizona Cardinals. 
Listen to the presser at 1090 AM or stream the entire presser here. Stream it: Audio 1 | Audio 2 | Video | Ravens News
